            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p xml:lang="heb">הדה נפשה ד<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>
               <lb/>ברה <supplied reason="lost">ד</supplied>עארון דמי<supplied reason="lost">ת</supplied>
               <lb/>בעסרה יומין בירח<lb/>כסליו בשת<supplied reason="lost">ה</supplied> חמישתה<lb/>דשאבועה דה<supplied reason="lost">י</supplied>
                    שנת<lb/>חמישת מאה ותשע שנין<lb/>לֹּחרבן בית מקדשה<lb/>שיבן ביומינן <supplied reason="lost">י</supplied>הי<lb/>משכבה בשלום</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>This is the tombstone [of ...],<lb/>son [of] Aaron(?), who died <lb/>on the tenth
                    day of the month<lb/>Kislev, in the fifth year<lb/>of the seven-year cycle,
                    which is the year<lb/>five hundred and nine years<lb/>of the destruction of the
                    Sanctuary.<lb/>May it be (re)built in our days.<lb/>May his resting place be in
                    peace.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p> Many letters and words are in parentheses, added by editor, for no clear reason.
                    Line 8 is written in Hebrew. Dated either to 10 Kislev 509 E.D.S., 4th S.Y. =  6
                    November 577 C.E. or to 10 kislev 509/510 E.D.S. 5th S.Y. = 25 November 578 CE. </p>
            </div>
        </body>
